Sure, here are some example sentences in Serbian that use the word "prilikom" in different forms and positions, with translations in English:

1. Prilikom posete gradu, posetili smo i muzej. (*Prilikom* = During) (During our visit to the city, we also visited the museum.)

2. Uzela sam sve potrebne stvari *prilikom* izlaska iz kuće. (*Prilikom* = When) (I took all the necessary things when leaving the house.)

3. Sve informacije su nam dostupne *prilikom* prijave. (*Prilikom* = Upon) (All information is available to us upon registration.)

4. *Prilikom* kupovine, obratite pažnju na rok trajanja proizvoda. (*Prilikom* = When) (When buying, pay attention to the expiration date of the product.)

5. Nisam se setio da ponesem novčanik *prilikom* izlaska iz kuće. (*Prilikom* = When) (I forgot to bring my wallet when leaving the house.)

6. Molim vas da *prilikom* popunjavanja obrasca pažljivo pročitate sva uputstva. (*Prilikom* = During) (Please carefully read all instructions during the form filling process.)

7. *Prilikom* pisanja diplomskog rada, potrebno je voditi računa o pravilima citiranja. (*Prilikom* = During) (During writing a thesis, it is necessary to follow the citation rules.)

8. *Prilikom* dolaska u restoran, slobodno izaberite sto koji vam najviše odgovara. (*Prilikom* = Upon) (Upon arrival at the restaurant, feel free to choose the table that suits you best.)